{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji49.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于革命派的大联合","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于革命派的大联合"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1967年4月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目前全国斗争形势很好，成绩很大，经验很多，全国都在前进中。革命派在优势情况下，可按系统、按部门、按单位。但要注意保守派把造反派吃掉，不要用解散革命造反派的办法实行大联合。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":4}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":430,"page_end":430},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}